My family hired the Real London Bus to help us out with transporting the fam for a family reunion.  We got the cute Pink Cheeky Bus! The driver Pat arrived early and was very helpful with taking a group photo of everyone in front of the bus. We were able to play our own music and bring beverages onboard. Overall, it was lots of fun and really fun for our relatives from out of town. I would definately recommend to friends and family!!

