R06GqtQo1UuvY1W9rNR2rA
I went in last Saturday to purchase a battery for my vehicle. Upon entry, we were greeted by Ed  who asked us if we had purchased the old battery from there. Of course we could not remember so we proceeded to pick out the new battery and brought to the counter. Ed then looked up our number and found out that we had bought the old one their and that it was still on warranty. My bill went from being $130 to $2.16 all thanks to Ed. Great store and honest!

