I've used them for my kids birthday 2 years in a row. It was a great experience every time. The customer service is excellent from the website, to the office, to the delivery guys. The jumper was clean and fairly priced. The delivery and pick up has always been right on time. I definitely would recommend them to anyone. Be nice and tip the delivery guys, but also what they would like most is a cold bottle of water.

